---

<section class="lm-teaser section" aria-label="Lifestyle Medicine">
  <div class="container lm-inner">
    <div class="lm-content">
      <span class="section-label">What Makes Us Unique</span>
      <h2>Most Doctors Tell You to Eat Better and Exercise More. We Show You How.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p>
        Lifestyle medicine is an evidence-based clinical specialty focused on preventing,
        treating, and reversing chronic disease through personalized changes in nutrition,
        movement, sleep, and stress. Dr. Lieberman isn't just familiar with this approach
        — he's board-certified in it, has developed formal training curricula for other
        physicians, and brings a background in culinary arts and nutrition science that
        makes the practical side of lifestyle change genuinely achievable.
      </p>
      <p>
        At Forward Family Medicine, lifestyle medicine isn't a handout at checkout.
        It's built into how we practice.
      </p>
      <div class="lm-highlights">
        <div class="lm-highlight">
          <span class="lm-highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">🎓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Board-Certified</strong>
            <span>American College of Lifestyle Medicine</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-highlight">
          <span class="lm-highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">🍴</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Culinary Arts + Nutrition Science</strong>
            <span>Pre-medical training in food and metabolism</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-highlight">
          <span class="lm-highlight-icon" aria-hidden="true">📋</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Built a Physician Training Curriculum</strong>
            <span>Dr. Lieberman trained other physicians in Lifestyle Medicine</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/lifestyle-medicine" class="btn btn-primary lm-cta">
        Learn About Our Lifestyle Medicine Approach →
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="lm-callout card">
      <h3>The Only Practice on the Main Line With This</h3>
      <p class="lm-callout-lead">
        No other local DPC practice offers it at all. We offer it in person, integrated into every visit — included in your membership.
      </p>
      <ul class="prose-list">
        <li>Personalized nutrition guidance from a culinary-trained physician</li>
        <li>Evidence-based protocols for diabetes, hypertension &amp; heart health</li>
        <li>Physical activity planning that fits your real life</li>
        <li>Sleep optimization and stress management</li>
        <li>Ongoing accountability — not a one-time conversation</li>
        <li>No extra fee — included in your DPC membership</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lm-teaser {
    background: var(--cream-100);
  }
  .lm-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .lm-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .lm-content p {
    color: var(--ink-700);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .lm-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.75rem 0;
  }
  .lm-highlight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .lm-highlight-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.1rem;
  }
  .lm-highlight strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .lm-highlight span {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-300);
  }
  .lm-cta {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Callout card */
  .lm-callout {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-50) 0%, var(--cream-200) 100%);
    border: 2px solid var(--green-300);
  }
  .lm-callout h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .lm-callout-lead {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .lm-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .lm-callout {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
